window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The future is a dangerous place </b></p> <p>Commander Joe Pikeman is on a mission he didn’t ask for…and wasn’t ordered on.&nbsp;</p> <p>Then again, he isn’t in the mood to sit back while Fairfax takes over the galaxy, either.&nbsp;</p> <p>Fairfax’s power stretches across the stars, and he’s calling in all his favors. From sparking a bot rebellion to engineering godlike monsters to crush his enemies, he seems determined to ruin Joe’s day.&nbsp;</p> <p>But he made one mistake: he screwed with Joe’s family. And as messed up as they are, that simply isn’t something Joe can allow.&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Download </b><b><i>Unsung Armada</i></b><b> now and jump into the military sci-fi action.</b>&nbsp;</p>"; 
